In [44]:
def mymodel(model):
    
    model.fit(xtrain,ytrain)
    ypred = model.predict(xtest)
    mae = mean_absolute_error(ytest,ypred)
    mse = mean_squared_error(ytest,ypred)
    rmse = np.sqrt(mse)
    r2 = r2_score(ytest,ypred)
    print(f"MAE : {mae}\nMSE : {mse}\nRMSE : {rmse}\nAccuracy : {r2}" )
    return model
